reviewText: My copy was damaged. So I purchased another one on eBay and the movie was interesting and on point with the director and creators style.
These guys talk about the sex, they had with other guys, they do have sex in this film, as they talk about themselves, and how other people perceive them.
A very interesting movie. The viewer gets a chance to peek into the private domain of the characters in the movie. Some rooms were more interesting than the others.
